Added the [delete onlineMeeting](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/onlinemeeting-delete.md) operation.

Changed return type for [mute](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/call-mute?view=graph-rest-beta) and [mute participant](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/participant-mute?view=graph-rest-beta) methods from [commsOperation](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/commsoperation?view=graph-rest-beta) to [muteParticipantOperation](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/muteparticipantoperation?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added new action [updateRecordingStatus](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/call-updaterecordingstatus?view=graph-rest-beta) to [call](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/call?view=graph-rest-beta) entity.

Renamed the **subcode** property to **subCode** on the [resultInfo](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/resultInfo?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
